  "description": "Random arc, 8 seconds, peak 0.7. LFO1 rapidly morphs vowels while LFO2 modulates vibrato depth — the voice wobbles and shifts like a hallucination. High ResSens creates phantom clusters during chaotic phases. The arc never fully resolves, leaving the listener in a perpetual state of almost-understanding. A fever dream where the choir speaks in tongues.",
